event: tool_result
data: {"name":"web_search","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"success\":true,\"query\":\"OpenAgentic GitHub repository site:github.com\",\"num_results\":10,\"results\":[{\"title\":\"GitHub - agentic-work/openagentic-sdk: OpenAgentic SDK - Direct LLM ...\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/agentic-work/openagentic-sdk\",\"snippet\":\"OpenAgenticSDK - Direct LLM provider access for agentic applications. Part of theOpenAgenticenterprise AI platform.\"},{\"title\":\"Agentic Authoring | GitHub Agentic Workflows\",\"url\":\"https://github.github.com/gh-aw/guides/agentic-authoring/\",\"snippet\":\"When you need to adapt an existing workflow from anotherrepository, use the create-agentic-agent to perform AI-assisted migration. The agent analyzes the source workflow, identifies dependencies, adapts configuration for yourrepository, and validates the result.\"},{\"title\":\"Awesome Agentic Workflow Repository - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/irfanfadhullah/Awesome-Agentic-Workflow\",\"snippet\":\"A curated collection ofGitHubrepositories focused on agentic workflows, autonomous agents, multi-agent systems, and AI workflow automation. Thisrepositoryserves as a comprehensive resource hub containing summarized documentation from projects related to intelligent agent frameworks and automated workflow orchestration.\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - agentic-work/oats: OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs ...\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats\",\"snippet\":\"OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs synthesize and execute one-shot tools with mandatory human approval. No static tool registration. No implicit trust. - agentic-work/oats\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - github/gh-aw: GitHub Agentic Workflows\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/github/gh-aw\",\"snippet\":\"See the Security Architecture for comprehensive details on threat modeling, implementation guidelines, and best practices. Using agentic workflows in yourrepositoryrequires careful attention to security considerations and careful human supervision, and even then things can still go wrong. Use it with caution, and at your own risk.\"},{\"title\":\"Network Graph · agentic-work/oats · GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats/network\",\"snippet\":\"Network graph Timeline of the most recent commits to thisrepositoryand its network ordered by most recently pushed to.\"},{\"title\":\"Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook\",\"snippet\":\"Folders and files ...Repositoryfiles navigationOpenAgenticPlaybook A playbook that sits on top of OpenClaw to make any agent more effective. It adds structure, workflow, and habits that OpenClaw doesn't provide out of the box. This is additive. It doesn't replace anything — it adds to what's already there.\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - supercog-ai/agentic: An opinionated framework for building ...\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/supercog-ai/agentic\",\"snippet\":\"Agentic makes it easy to create AI agents - autonomous software programs that understand natural language and can use tools to do work on your behalf. Agentic is in the tradition of opinionated frameworks. We've tried to encode lots of sensible defaults and best practices into the design, testing and deployment of agents. Agentic is a few different things: A lightweight agent framework. Same ...\"},{\"title\":\"# Agentic AI Learning Repository This repository contains ... - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/Muhammadzeeshan-dev/Agentic-AI\",\"snippet\":\"About # Agentic AI LearningRepository🚀 Thisrepositorycontains my practice work, experiments, and mini projects focused on building Agentic AI systems from scratch. Currently starting from basics and gradually moving towards advanced multi-agent systems.\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - agentic-framework/agentic: Agentic new world\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/agentic-framework/agentic\",\"snippet\":\"Thisrepositorycontains rules, guidelines, and tools for allowing AI agents to operate on a machine with significant freedom while maintaining security, organization, and best practices.\"}],\"source\":\"duckduckgo-html\",\"tip\":\"Use web_fetch to read the full content of any interesting result\"}"}],"structuredContent":{"success":true,"query":"OpenAgentic GitHub repository site:github.com","num_results":10,"results":[{"title":"GitHub - agentic-work/openagentic-sdk: OpenAgentic SDK - Direct LLM ...","url":"https://github.com/agentic-work/openagentic-sdk","snippet":"OpenAgenticSDK - Direct LLM provider access for agentic applications. Part of theOpenAgenticenterprise AI platform."},{"title":"Agentic Authoring | GitHub Agentic Workflows","url":"https://github.github.com/gh-aw/guides/agentic-authoring/","snippet":"When you need to adapt an existing workflow from anotherrepository, use the create-agentic-agent to perform AI-assisted migration. The agent analyzes the source workflow, identifies dependencies, adapts configuration for yourrepository, and validates the result."},{"title":"Awesome Agentic Workflow Repository - GitHub","url":"https://github.com/irfanfadhullah/Awesome-Agentic-Workflow","snippet":"A curated collection ofGitHubrepositories focused on agentic workflows, autonomous agents, multi-agent systems, and AI workflow automation. Thisrepositoryserves as a comprehensive resource hub containing summarized documentation from projects related to intelligent agent frameworks and automated workflow orchestration."},{"title":"GitHub - agentic-work/oats: OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs ...","url":"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats","snippet":"OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs synthesize and execute one-shot tools with mandatory human approval. No static tool registration. No implicit trust. - agentic-work/oats"},{"title":"GitHub - github/gh-aw: GitHub Agentic Workflows","url":"https://github.com/github/gh-aw","snippet":"See the Security Architecture for comprehensive details on threat modeling, implementation guidelines, and best practices. Using agentic workflows in yourrepositoryrequires careful attention to security considerations and careful human supervision, and even then things can still go wrong. Use it with caution, and at your own risk."},{"title":"Network Graph · agentic-work/oats · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats/network","snippet":"Network graph Timeline of the most recent commits to thisrepositoryand its network ordered by most recently pushed to."},{"title":"Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook - GitHub","url":"https://github.com/Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook","snippet":"Folders and files ...Repositoryfiles navigationOpenAgenticPlaybook A playbook that sits on top of OpenClaw to make any agent more effective. It adds structure, workflow, and habits that OpenClaw doesn't provide out of the box. This is additive. It doesn't replace anything — it adds to what's already there."},{"title":"GitHub - supercog-ai/agentic: An opinionated framework for building ...","url":"https://github.com/supercog-ai/agentic","snippet":"Agentic makes it easy to create AI agents - autonomous software programs that understand natural language and can use tools to do work on your behalf. Agentic is in the tradition of opinionated frameworks. We've tried to encode lots of sensible defaults and best practices into the design, testing and deployment of agents. Agentic is a few different things: A lightweight agent framework. Same ..."},{"title":"# Agentic AI Learning Repository This repository contains ... - GitHub","url":"https://github.com/Muhammadzeeshan-dev/Agentic-AI","snippet":"About # Agentic AI LearningRepository🚀 Thisrepositorycontains my practice work, experiments, and mini projects focused on building Agentic AI systems from scratch. Currently starting from basics and gradually moving towards advanced multi-agent systems."},{"title":"GitHub - agentic-framework/agentic: Agentic new world","url":"https://github.com/agentic-framework/agentic","snippet":"Thisrepositorycontains rules, guidelines, and tools for allowing AI agents to operate on a machine with significant freedom while maintaining security, organization, and best practices."}],"source":"duckduckgo-html","tip":"Use web_fetch to read the full content of any interesting result"},"isError":false},"toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_017PVuGtMiA3nGsfQX6x5amN","executionTimeMs":801,"targetServer":"openagentic_web","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:37:40.199Z"}

