tonomous agents, multi-agent systems, and AI workflow automation. Thisrepositoryserves as a comprehensive resource hub containing summarized documentation from projects related to intelligent agent frameworks and automated workflow orchestration."},{"title":"GitHub - agentic-work/oats: OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs ...","url":"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats","snippet":"OATS — On-demand Agent Tool Synthesis. LLMs synthesize and execute one-shot tools with mandatory human approval. No static tool registration. No implicit trust. - agentic-work/oats"},{"title":"GitHub - github/gh-aw: GitHub Agentic Workflows","url":"https://github.com/github/gh-aw","snippet":"See the Security Architecture for comprehensive details on threat modeling, implementation guidelines, and best practices. Using agentic workflows in yourrepositoryrequires careful attention to security considerations and careful human supervision, and even then things can still go wrong. Use it with caution, and at your own risk."},{"title":"Network Graph · agentic-work/oats · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/agentic-work/oats/network","snippet":"Network graph Timeline of the most recent commits to thisrepositoryand its network ordered by most recently pushed to."},{"title":"Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook - GitHub","url":"https://github.com/Stephane-fci/agentic-work-playbook","snippet":"Folders and files ...Repositoryfiles navigationOpenAgenticPlaybook A playbook that sits on top of OpenClaw to make any agent more effective. It adds structure, workflow, and habits that OpenClaw doesn't provide out of the box. This is additive. It doesn't replace anything — it adds to what's already there."},{"title":"GitHub - supercog-ai/agentic: An opinionated framework for building ...","url":"https://github.com/supercog-ai/agentic","snippet":"Agentic makes it easy to create AI agents - autonomous software programs that understand natural language and can use tools to do work on your behalf. Agentic is 